title: 'GM Street' — Initial Impressions From Week 1 (Ep. 140)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier huddle up to discuss whether or not Trevor Siemian can save the Broncos (02:30), a new-look Raiders defense (05:00), a victorious yet unhappy Joe Flacco (13:30), and the top draft prospects in college football (19:00).
